---
import Layout from '~/layouts/PageLayout.astro';

const metadata = {
  title: 'About Dr. Leonid Lurie',
};
---

<Layout metadata={metadata}>
  <section class="px-4 sm:px-6 py-14 sm:py-20 mx-auto max-w-6xl">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-10 items-start">
      <div>
        <p class="text-sm font-medium text-accent">About</p>
        <h1 class="mt-3 text-3xl sm:text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight">About Dr. Leonid Lurie</h1>
        <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-muted">Physician–scientist, biophysicist, and formulation technology developer.</p>
        <p class="mt-5 text-muted max-w-2xl">
          Dr. Leonid Lurie works at the intersection of medicine, biophysics, and advanced delivery systems, developing
          science-led formulation platforms for health, hygiene, and skin-related applications.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div
          class="rounded-2xl border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-800 overflow-hidden bg-gray-50 dark:bg-slate-900"
        >
          <img
            src="/images/dr-lurie-portrait.jpg"
            alt="Portrait of Dr. Leonid Lurie"
            class="w-full h-auto object-cover"
            loading="lazy"
            onerror="this.style.display='none'; this.nextElementSibling.style.display='flex';"
          />
          <div class="hidden items-center justify-center min-h-[420px] p-8 text-center text-muted">
            Add portrait image at <code class="mx-1">public/images/dr-lurie-portrait.jpg</code>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="px-4 sm:px-6 py-12 mx-auto max-w-4xl border-t border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-800">
    <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight">Core Positioning</h2>
    <p class="mt-4 text-muted">
      Dr. Lurie’s contribution is not limited to individual formulas. His work emphasizes a structured methodology for
      delivery systems that can be translated into targeted, scalable, real-world products.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="px-4 sm:px-6 py-12 mx-auto max-w-4xl">
    <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight">Scientific and Medical Approach</h2>
    <p class="mt-4 text-muted">
      <strong class="text-default">The skin is not a passive surface. It is a dynamic biological system.</strong> This principle
      informs how problems are defined, how active compounds are selected, and how formulation design is executed for better
      biological relevance.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="px-4 sm:px-6 py-12 mx-auto max-w-4xl border-t border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-800">
    <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight">Technology Platform and Delivery Systems</h2>
    <p class="mt-4 text-muted">
      The platform approach is based on structured carrier systems and lipid-oriented architectures designed to improve
      functional performance in practical use.
    </p>
    <ul class="mt-5 list-disc pl-5 space-y-2 text-default">
      <li>Targeted interaction with biological sites</li>
      <li>Controlled release of active compounds</li>
      <li>Protection of active ingredients through delivery</li>
      <li>Enhanced penetration support without invasive methods</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section class="px-4 sm:px-6 py-12 mx-auto max-w-4xl">
    <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight">Credibility</h2>
    <div class="mt-6 grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
      <article class="rounded-xl border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-800 p-5 bg-white dark:bg-slate-900">
        <h3 class="font-semibold">Education</h3>
        <ul class="mt-3 list-disc pl-5 space-y-1 text-sm text-muted">
          <li>M.D.</li>
          <li>Ph.D. in biophysics</li>
          <li>Weizmann Institute of Science background</li>
        </ul>
      </article>
      <article class="rounded-xl border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-800 p-5 bg-white dark:bg-slate-900">
        <h3 class="font-semibold">Professional Experience</h3>
        <ul class="mt-3 list-disc pl-5 space-y-1 text-sm text-muted">
          <li>30+ years in pharmaceutical and biotechnology development</li>
          <li>CTO / Executive Director of Formulation roles</li>
          <li>R&amp;D leadership, clinical and regulatory development experience</li>
        </ul>
      </article>
      <article class="rounded-xl border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-800 p-5 bg-white dark:bg-slate-900">
        <h3 class="font-semibold">Innovation</h3>
        <ul class="mt-3 list-disc pl-5 space-y-1 text-sm text-muted">
          <li>Multiple international patents</li>
          <li>Modular delivery-system platform</li>
        </ul>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="px-4 sm:px-6 py-12 mx-auto max-w-4xl border-t border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-800">
    <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight">Applications and Case Experience</h2>
    <ul class="mt-5 list-disc pl-5 space-y-2 text-default">
      <li>Medical and para-medical delivery systems</li>
      <li>Hygiene and public-health applications</li>
      <li>Cosmeceutical and skin-related applications</li>
      <li>Licensing, co-development, and technology collaboration models</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section class="px-4 sm:px-6 py-12 mx-auto max-w-4xl">
    <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight">Philosophy and Vision</h2>
    <p class="mt-4 text-muted">
      <strong class="text-default"
        >Effective products emerge from the alignment of science, formulation, and real-world use.</strong
      >
      Formulation is the interface between scientific understanding and everyday human experience.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="px-4 sm:px-6 py-14 mx-auto max-w-6xl border-t border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-800">
    <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight">Start With the Science</h2>
    <p class="mt-4 text-muted max-w-3xl">
      Explore how aging skin changes, why common approaches often fall short, and what a delivery-system approach makes
      possible.
    </p>
    <div class="mt-8 flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-3">
      <a class="btn-primary" href="/blog">Read the Insights</a>
      <a class="btn-secondary" href="/#guide">Get the Free Guide</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
